    • Method Detail

      • cascadingCut

        public void cascadingCut(Node min)
        Cuts this from its parent and then does the same for its parent and continues all the way to the top of the tree in same manner.
        Parameters:
        min - heaps minimum node, to which other nodes will be added.

      • cut

        public void cut(Node node,
                Node min)
        Removes the node from the child list of this node.
        Parameters:
        node - child to be removed from this node's child list
        min - the minimum heap node, to which x is added.

      • link

        public void link(Node parent)
        Make this node a child of the given parent node. All links are updated, parents degree is incremented and mark is set to false.
        Parameters:
        parent - the new parent node.
